102.4	Chuck_Klosterman	Chuck Klosterman	Charles John "Chuck" Klosterman (born June 5, 1972) is an American author and essayist who has written for The New York Times Magazine, The Believer, and The Washington Post, and has written books focusing on American popular culture.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/8/80/Chuck_Klosterman_at_the_Brooklyn_Book_Festival.jpg/220px-Chuck_Klosterman_at_the_Brooklyn_Book_Festival.jpg
